<L>__{interior hotel room day}
<A>__{the door to the room opens and the bellboy, followed by zed, walks into the room. he puts zed's bag onto one of those luggage holders and proceeds to show him the room. sitting on the bed is a large air freight package.}
<C>__{bellboy}
<P>__{(in broken english)}
<D>__{your package...it arrived in the last night of before last night.}
