<C>__{bellboy}
<D>__{from here you can operate the television.}
<A>__{then he pauses at the door before he goes out. zed reaches into his pocket and takes out some french money, he starts fingering through it. then, the bellboy takes the liberty of showing zed which bills to give him.}
