<D>__{time.}
<C>__{bellboy}
<D>__{ah. yes. il est presque huit heures moins dix.}
<A>__{the bellboy clicks his heels and walks out the door. zed looks around the room, still wondering what time it is, and takes a seat on the bed. obviously tired from the flight zed unbuttons his shirt a bit and lays back on the bed next to the package. before he dozes off to sleep he takes his watch off and places it on the bedside table. he is asleep.}
